gamerule.allowIceBoatSpeed: Allow boats to speed up on ice-like blocks
gamerule.horseStaminaTicks: Amount of ticks horses are allowed to sprint before getting exhausted
gamerule.horseExhaustDebuff: Percent of movement speed to remove when horse gets exhausted
gamerule.horseSprintBuff: Percent of movement speed to add when horse is sprinting
gamerule.horseStaminaRegenTicks: Amount of ticks to add back to stamina per tick of not sprinting
